%% docs/diagrams/screen-layouts/screen-flow-v1.mmd
flowchart LR
  %% v1 Screen Flow (poc-purchasing-approval) - Left to Right

  Login[Login]
  Home[Home / Dashboard<br/>申請一覧]
  NewForm[新規申請作成]
  NewConfirm[新規申請確認]
  Detail[申請詳細]

  %% Basic navigation
  Login -->|ログイン成功| Home

  %% Create flow (input -> confirm -> submit)
  Home -->|新規作成| NewForm
  NewForm -->|確認| NewConfirm
  NewConfirm -->|提出（submit）成功| Detail

  %% Create flow back
  NewForm -->|キャンセル| Home
  NewConfirm -->|戻る| NewForm

  %% List -> Detail
  Home -->|申請を選択| Detail
  Detail -->|一覧へ戻る| Home

  %% Role-based behaviors (notes)
  subgraph RoleBased[申請詳細画面でのロール別表示]
    direction TB
    Applicant[申請者: コメント投稿可 / 内容閲覧 / （RETURNED時のみ）編集・再提出]
    Approver[承認者: コメント投稿可 + AI要約表示 + 承認/差し戻し（PENDING時）]
  end

  Detail -.-> Applicant
  Detail -.-> Approver
